column5: Do they have their huts in a good location,?  Looking to book with them for a few days midweek with a buddy and our 12 year old sons,thought the satelite tv might come in handy for the boys during slow times and evenings,plus a little tsn would not be so bad either.
I haven't used them in years but we did well with them the times we did use them.  I believe it may be new owners since the last time I was there but not sure.
